      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can u expand on the part about it being a 'moral imperative'? like, how do i frame the argument so it sounds like the opposite view—you know, the meritocracy argument—is basically just a way to ignore systemic racism? i want to make sure those counter-arguments look weak in my essay.",
